code: /**  * Return the {@link DataUnit} matching the specified {@code suffix}.  * @param suffix one of the standard suffix  * @return the {@link DataUnit} matching the specified {@code suffix}  * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the suffix does not match any  * of this enum's constants  */ public static DataUnit fromSuffix(String suffix) {     for (DataUnit candidate : values()) {         if (Objects.equals(candidate.suffix, suffix)) {             return candidate.         }     }     throw new IllegalArgumentException("Unknown unit '" + suffix + "'"). }
